Package: fastEmbedR
Type: Package
Title: Fast Native UMAP and openTSNE from Precomputed KNN Matrices
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Stefano",
    family = "User",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "stefano@example.com")
Author: Stefano User [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Stefano User <stefano@example.com>
Description: A compact UMAP and openTSNE-style implementation focused on fast
    embeddings from precomputed nearest-neighbor index and distance matrices.
    Nearest-neighbor search, preprocessing helpers, fixed-reference transform,
    and stochastic layout optimization are implemented in native code with a
    user-facing API centered on fast KNN reuse and explicit CPU/Metal/CUDA
    backend reporting.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/tkcaccia/fastEmbedR
BugReports: https://github.com/tkcaccia/fastEmbedR/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
