SystemRequirements: C++17, Fortran, optional FAISS C++ library for backend = "faiss", optional RAPIDS cuVS library for backend = "cuda_cuvs", Metal framework on macOS for the optional Metal backend, CUDA toolkit for the optional CUDA backend
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
